					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">MMC1 CHR banks are 4 KiB in size. Which CHR switching mode (8 KiB or 4 KiB) are you using, so that I can explain in more detail?
<br />
<br />You usually do not want to reset the MMC1 before each sequence of 5 writes, except in the reset handler. Resetting the MMC1 has the side effect of setting the PRG switching mode to 16 KiB, upper bank fixed.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

