				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">This is a normal behavior of the MMC1 (and most other mappers exept MMC5), the banks (be them PRG or CHR) are "numbered" by the smaller available size, and if a larger size is used, lower bits are ignored.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
					<br clear="all" /><br />

