				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Almost. The 8 KiB mode switches bank (n &amp; $1E) into $0000 and bank (n | $01) into $1000. This means you can't use it to, say, switch bank 1 into $0000 and 2 into $1000; you need 4 KiB mode for that.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

